only provides functionality comparable to
.IR OpenSS7
for use by
.I STREAMS
drivers and modules.
Any and all functionality provided by
.BR mi_timer_cond ()
in support of
.RI non- STREAMS
devices are not supported.
.PP
See
.BR os7compat (9),
.BR mpscompat (9),
.BR suncompat (9),
.BR maccompat (9),
and
.BR STREAMS (9)
for additional compatibility considerations.
.\"
